title: November 2018 Q&A
description:
Every month I do a Q&A for patrons. Since this month I deal with a lot of controversy that has been floating around,  I thought I would put it up for all of you to watch.  I deal with attacks on JBP, my thoughts on the resurrection and many other sparks we have recently seen flying. 

For a montly Q&A, join me on Patreon.

My links:  

patreon: https://www.patreon.com/pageauvideos
paypal: https://www.paypal.me/JonathanPageau

The podcast: https://soundcloud.com/jonathan-pagea...
website: http://www.thesymbolicworld.com
facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheSymbolicW...
twitter: https://twitter.com/pageaujonathan
